_sText:
As seen in AcePerrys upcoming map.

There is an invisible button, place the button in your map where you want to press, make sure you remember, I recommend it being next to the dumpster so you know when people are in there, then press it. No way out for the prisoners :)
Even kills in RPG server, gives 500hp, which is max hp on RPG.
There is a ladder to get in, but I suggest putting some boxes next to it, so people can jump in.
